data.description: GULFGATE AREA - NEAR BROADWAY & 610 LOOP - House - Garage Apartment -&- Vacant Lot at the Corner of Metcalf & Browne - 3 Lots - 15,000 SF - 150' on Metcalf - 100' on Browne - House at 2639 Metcalf is a 2BR-1BTH -  Garage Apartment at 2637 Metcalf has Two 1BR-1BTH Units above a 4-Car Garage - Plus the adjacent Vacant Lot -    House rents for $850/Mo and apartments each rent for $750/Mo - 100% Occupied - Long Term Tenants  Please Do Not Walk the Property or Disturb the Tenants - Appointment Required
